title: #92Noon! Micheletti/SafetyDance/Lavelle
description: Pat Micheletti joins for the entire first hour to celebrate the NCAA Hockey tourney that now has three MN teams in the Frozen Four, Vikings talkers for most of the middle hour, then Lavelle joins for the final stretch!
